Cute Three-Photo Pre-School Graduation for Girl Invitation

Big Deals! Cute Three-Photo Pre-School Graduation for Girl Invitation – Graduation Invitations Popular Cute Three-Photo Pre-School Graduation for Girl Invitation It’s a great choice Cute Three-Photo Pre-School Graduation for Girl Invitation See more about itDelight your pre-school graduate with a celebration to mark the occasion using this cute girly photo invitation with an easy to use three-photo template. Insert your three desired photos in place of the sample photos used in this design. Tip: square photos work best, i.e. Instagram photos. Edit the sample text with your desired details. Pretty pink sketched watercolor flowers and stripes add trendy style to this design. Since all of the text in this announcement/invitation may be edited, you can also use it for other types of parties or events for any age. Price:$2.09
